%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6787dd3450dfd88e193e8a20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20food%20on%20the%20Seabourn%20Pursuit%20was%20quite%20tasty.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Morris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20days%2C%20we%20had%20breakfast%20and%20lunch%20at%20onboard%20restaurant%20The%20Colonnade.%20These%20meals%20were%20served%20buffet-style%2C%20though%20we%20could%20also%20order%20eggs%20or%20daily%20specials%20from%20the%20waitstaff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20dining%20room%2C%20The%20Restaurant%2C%20offered%20waiter%20service%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20most%20part%2C%20the%20food%20on%20our%20trip%20was%20quite%20good%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20considering%20we%20were%20essentially%20on%20a%20floating%20base%20camp%20for%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-live-on-cruise-look-inside-my-room-wraparound-balcony-photos-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoom%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20also%20available%2024%2F7%2C%20which%20we%20often%20took%20advantage%20of%20during%20rough%20seas.%20I%20loved%20that%20we%20could%20order%20caviar%20anytime%20and%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20spent%20time%20at%20the%20onboard%20lounge%20The%20Club%2C%20where%20we%20could%20listen%20to%20live%20music%20and%20order%20a%20selection%20of%20nigiri%2C%20sashimi%2C%20and%20rolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHowever%2C%20the%20real%20highlight%20of%20the%20cruise%20was%20all%20of%20the%20adventure.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20David%20Morris%20and%20his%20mom%20in%20Antarctica%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6787dd35e294a7514e8d3dee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20mom%20and%20I%20were%20excited%20about%20the%20many%20excursions%20on%20the%20cruise.%3Cp%3EDavi