Perhaps%20the%20most%20incredible%20part%20of%20the%20trip%20was%20peering%20below%20the%20ocean%20floor%20in%20one%20of%20the%20ship's%20two%20submersibles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftitan-submersible-implosion-1-year-investigators-miss-12-month-deadline-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOceanGate%20submersible%20disaster%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20I%20was%20nervous%20to%20set%20foot%20in%20one%20of%20these%20vehicles.%20However%2C%20our%20pilots%20thoroughly%20explained%20the%20submersible%20technology%20and%20how%20it%20was%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20noted%20we%20were%20descending%20only%20300%20meters%20%E2%80%94%20OceanGate's%20vessel%20had%20attempted%20to%20go%20thousands%20of%20meters%20underwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReassured%2C%20I%20took%20a%20Zodiac%20to%20the%20sub%2C%20then%20climbed%20down%20a%20short%2C%20three-rung%20ladder%20into%20the%20craft%2C%20which%20holds%20up%20to%20six%20guests%20and%20a%20pilot.%20I%20found%20it%20surprisingly%20easy%20to%20navigate%20getting%20in%20and%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20under%20the%20water%2C%20the%20experience%20felt%20otherworldly.%20We%20observed%20a%20variety%20of%20invertebrates%20on%20the%20seafloor%2C%20and%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20polar%20gigantism%2C%20where%20animals%20living%20in%20the%20poles%20are%20far%20bigger%20than%20their%20counterparts%20near%20the%20equator%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20my%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20cruise%20ship%20with%20a%20smaller%20boat%20of%20people%20sailing%20away%20from%20it%20in%20front%20of%20a%20snowy%20backdrop%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6787dd3350dfd88e193e8a1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20saw%20so%20much%20beauty%20on%20our%20Seabourn%20Pursuit%20cruise.%3Cp%3E%20John%20Sedgw