22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6769b9fbe3e473ef263ad40c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%209%C3%9712%20rugs%20come%20with%20a%20two-piece%20pad%20that%20was%20a%20bit%20tricky%20to%20set%20up%20in%20our%20dining%20room.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERuggable%20rugs%20come%20as%20two%20pieces%3A%20the%20cover%20(which%20is%20the%20rug%20itself)%20and%20the%20rug%20pad.%20To%20set%20up%20a%20rug%2C%20you%20have%20to%20first%20lay%20down%20the%20pad%2C%20then%20unroll%20the%20cover%20onto%20the%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rug%20covers%20come%20rolled%20up%20with%20the%20decorative%20side%20facing%20outwards.%20The%20instructions%20say%20to%20unroll%20the%20rug%20and%20then%20re-roll%20it%20so%20the%20decorative%20side%20is%20facing%20inward.%20Once%20you%20re-roll%20the%20cover%2C%20you%20unroll%20it%20over%20the%20pad%2C%20being%20careful%20to%20perfectly%20align%20the%20corners%20and%20edges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20big%20open%20space%20to%20unroll%20and%20re-roll%20the%20rug%20cover%2C%20setup%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20large%20rugs.%20When%20setting%20up%20a%209x12%20rug%20in%20our%20enclosed%20dining%20room%2C%20we%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20work%20around%20our%20heavy%2C%208-person%20table%2C%20which%20we%20couldn't%20remove%20from%20the%20room.%20We%20had%20to%20get%20scrappy%20and%20re-roll%20the%20rug%20while%20holding%20it%20in%20the%20air.%20It%20was%20also%20challenging%20getting%20the%20cover%20perfectly%20aligned%20with%20the%20pad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257fe7615-3cb0-4e82-9576-81256f98c839%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMost%20people%20I%20spoke%20to%20preferred%20using%20Ruggable%20rugs%20for%20high-traffic%20areas%20where%20they%20didn't%20have%20to%20move%20furniture%20in%20order%20to%20wash%20them.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20own%20experience%20and%20many%20conversations%20with%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D57071c1cdd98adc0f3091b5416aa52200a135e56e8189db98c9db2ce4b7c3f32%26postID%3D6769b6f3598acda0f94ce50b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fruggable-review-washable-rugs%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fruggable.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERuggable%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0owners%2C%20larger%20rugs%20that%20are%20covered%20by%20furniture%20rarely%20get%20washed%20because%20they're%20kind%20of%20a%20pain%20to%20remove%20and%20set%20back%20up.%20The%20real%20value%20in%20a%20Ruggable%20rug%20is%20when%20you%20use%20them%20in%20busy%20areas%20like%20hallways%20or%20kitchens%20because%20the%20rugs%20can%20easily%20be%20thrown%20in%20the%20wash%20and%20reset%20on%20their%20pads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20lots%20of%20people%20still%20love%20using%20them%20in%20their%20living%20rooms%20and%20don't%20mind%20the%20work%20of%20moving%20some%20furniture%20around%20to%20throw%20them%20in%20the%20wash.%20The%20author%20of%20our%20guide%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-area-rug%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20best%20area%20rugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20swears%20by%20the%20Ruggable%20in%20her%20living%20room%2C%20which%20she%20says%20had%20withstood%20plenty%20of%20spills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220abf5be6-f5f8-4916-8943-9e2ae132b85b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rugs%20really%20can%20be%20machine-washed%20and%20dried%2C%20but%20you%20should%20expect%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20fading%20over%20time.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dining%20room%20with%20a%20Ruggable%20rug%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6769bcf5e3e473ef263ad5b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20compliment%20our%20rug%20all%20the%20time%2C%20often%2C%20asking%20if%20it's%20vintage.%20Most%20of%20the%20other%20rugs%20in%20my%20house%20are%20vintage%2C%20but%20this%20one%20gives%20the%20same%20effect%20while%20being%20washable%20and%20soft.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERuggable%20rugs%20should%20be%20washed%20on%20a%20delicate%20cycle%20with%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20non-bleach%20detergent.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.ruggable.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F360053511633-How-do-I-wash-or-clean-my-Ruggable-rug%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERuggable's%20instructions%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0suggest%20adding%20a%20cup%20of%20vinegar%20to%20neutralize%20pet%20odors.%20To%20dry%2C%20use%20a%20low-heat%20setting%20on%20your%20dryer%2C%20and%20depending%20on%20the%20size%20of%20your%20rug%2C%20you%20may%20have%20to%20run%20the%20cycle%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20interviews%20with%20other%20Ruggable%20owners%2C%20the%20color%20and%20design%20hold%20up%20well%20against%20occasional%20washing%20and%20spot%20cleaning.%20There's%20no%20limit%20to%20how%20often%20you%20can%20wash%20your%20rug%2C%20though%20you%20should%20expect%20some%20fading%20over%20time%20if%20you%20wash%20it%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20wondering%20whether%20the%20rug%20size%20you're%20looking%20at%20will%20fit%20in%20your%20washing%20machine%2C%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D4f4f8008b20d4af0b5938d5198e56519bb5c3259d43ed0e18fcf133f4b3e9e4c%26postID%3D6769b6f3598acda0f94ce50b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fruggable-review-washable-rugs%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fruggable.com%252Fpages%252Fwashing-machine-rug-guide%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERuggable%20offers%20a%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20tells%20you%20the%20cubic%20feet%20your%20washer%20needs%20to%20be%20for%20the%20various%20sizes%20of%20rugs.%20For%20instance%2C%20my%209%20%C3%97%2012%20foot%20rug%20requires%20a%20washer%20drum%20that%20is%20at%20least