e%20opposition%20MPs%20sought%20to%20corner%20the%20government%20over%20a%20host%20of%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20spoken%20on%20Monday%2C%20slamming%20the%20government%20over%20its%20%26quot%3Bfailed%26quot%3B%20Make%20in%20India%20policy%20among%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%20quotes%20from%20PM's%20address%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20We%20have%20done%20so%20much%20for%20the%20poor%20people%20that%20the%20president%20spoke%20about%20it%20at%20length%20in%20his%20speech.%20Those%20who%20do%20photo%20ops%20in%20huts%2C%20they%20will%20find%20a%20discussion%20on%20poor%20people%20boring%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Some%20leaders%20are%20focusing%20on%20jacuzzies%20and%20stylish%20showers%2C%20but%20our%20focus%20is%20on%20getting%20a%20water%20connection%20in%20every%20home.%20Our%20govt%20gave%20tap%20water%20to%2012%20crore%20families%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20They%20used%20to%20ridicule%20our%20sanitation%20programme%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20We%20have%20removed%2010%20crore%20fake%20beneficiaries%20of%20government%20schemes%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Our%20model%20is%20'%3Cem%3Ebachat%20bhi%2C%20vikas%20bhi%3C%2Fem%3E'%20-%20%3Cem%3Ejanta%20ka%20paisa%2C%20janta%20ke%20liye%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20brought%20the%20scheme%20of%20direct%20benefit%20transfer.%20We%20deposited%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20crore%20directly%20into%20people's%20bank%20accounts%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20There%20was%20fashion%20to%20call%20one%20PM%20as%20Mr%20Clean%20but%20he%20admitted%20that%20if%20Re%201%20is%20sent%20from%20Delhi%2C%20people%20got%20only%2015%20paise%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20There's%20this%20WHO%20report%20which%20says%20due%20to%20'nal%20se%20jal'%20the%20family%20who%20used%20to%20spend%20on%20several%20diseases%2C%20they%20have%20saved%20crores%20of%20money%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Didn't%20use%20government%20money%20for%20Sheeshmahal%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20One%20PM%20used%20to%20repeat%20the%20word%2021st%20century%20a%20lot.%20RK%20Laxman%20drew%20an%20interesting%20cartoon%20then.%20In%20that%20cartoon%2C%20there%20was%20a%20plane%20and%20a%20pilot%20and%20the%20plane%20was%20on%20a%20cart%20and%20workers%20were%20pushing%20that%20cart%20and%2021st%20century%20was%20written%20on%20it%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20For%20some%20people%2C%20AI%20is%20a%20fashionable%20term.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20has%20dual%20meanings%20-%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20and%20Aspirational%20India.%20In%20this%20Budget%2C%20there%20is%20a%20provision%20for%2050%2C000%20new%20AI%20labs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20The%20country%20has%20seen%20in%20Haryana%20how%20we%20function.%20We%20promised%20jobs%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20our%20government%20was%20formed%20we%20gave%20jobs%20as%20promised%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20In%20Maharashtra%20too%20we%20registered%20a%20historic%20win%2C%20which%20was%20possible%20due%20to%20people's%20blessings%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20We%20are%20focusing%20on%20youth%20but%20some%20people%20are%20betraying%20them.%20This%20group%2C%20during%20elections%20promises%20many%20things%20but%20doesn't%20fulfil%20them.%20This%20group%20is%20an%20'AAP-da'%20on%20the%20future%20of%20the%20youth%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738671660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbc7dk8ng_pm-modi-parliament-650_625x300_10_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-reply-to-motion-of-thanks-on-presidents-address-7632425%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20underlined%20that%20his%20government%20has%20given%20true%20development%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20not%20empty%20slogans%20while%20he%20was%20replyingto%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20on%20the%20President's%20Address.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-to-reply-to