ltant%20and%20former%20Apple%20engineer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20cofounders%20said%20AI%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20growth%20for%20small-%20and%20midsize%20consultancies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EConsulting%20has%20long%20relied%20on%20manpower%2C%20but%20a%20new%20generative%20AI%20startup%20co-founded%20by%20a%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmbb-explained-mckinsey-bain-bcg-compare-big-three-strategy-consultants-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMcKinsey%20consultant%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20its%20software%20can%20take%20over%20some%20of%20the%20industry's%20most%20tedious%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20internal%20processes%20are%20extremely%20manual%20labor%20heavy%2C%26quot%3B%20Alibek%20Dostiyarov%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Perceptis%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firms-mckinsey-bcg-accenture-workers-leaving-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsulting%3C%2Fa%3E%20workflows%2C%20which%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Blend%20themselves%20almost%20perfectly%20to%20what%20GenAI%20is%20capable%20of%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20co-founded%20Perceptis%20with%20CTO%20Yersultan%20Sapar%2C%20a%20former%20engineer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-stock-earnings-call-report-live-updates-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20help%20consulting%20and%20professional%20services%20firms%20automate%20monotonous%20tasks%2C%20freeing%20up%20people%20at%20those%20firms%20to%20serve%20more%20clients%20and%20focus%20on%20solving%20their%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerceptis%20is%20an%20operating%20system%20for%20the%20consultants%20designed%20to%20help%20them%20win%20more%20business%20and%20make%20consulting%20%E2%80%94%20their%20day%20job%20%E2%80%94%20even%20more%20enjoyable%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20core%20of%20their%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20Sapar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptis%20has%20raised%20%243.6%20million%20in%20funding%20led%20by%20Streamlined%20Ventures%2C%20along%20with%20The%20House%20Fund%2C%20Tekton%20Ventures%2C%20FEBE%20Ventures%2C%20MOST%20Ventures%2C%20and%20Silkroad%20Innovation%20Hub.%20They've%20also%20gained%20some%20prominent%20angel%20investors%2C%20including%20Charlie%20Songhurst%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Meta's%20board%20of%20directors%20and%20former%20Microsoft%20executive%3B%20AJ%20Shankar%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Everlaw%2C%20and%20Peter%20Kazanjy%2C%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BFounding%20Sales%26quot%3B%20and%C2%A0co-founder%20of%C2%A0Atrium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvancements%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-wall-scaling-laws-training-data-chatgpt-gemini-claude-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20disrupted%20the%20broader%20consulting%20industry%2C%20with%20major%20firms%20making%20huge%20investments%20in%20the%20technology%20and%20establishing%20dedicated%20AI%20units%2C%20such%20as%20McKinsey's%20QuantumBlack.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-ai-consulting-focus-future-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esenior%20partner%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20McKinsey%20told%20BI%20last%20year%20that%20he%20thinks%20AI%20is%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20be%20most%20of%20what%20we%20do%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22efdb3487-6131-435b-a88b-39f1cece3398%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20helps%20consultants%20land%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptis%20is%20currently%20focused%20on%20the%20business%20development%20side%20of%20consulting%2C%20or%20helping%20firms%20secure%20jobs.%20The%20AI%20can%20do%20industry%20research%20for%20companies%20that%20Perceptis%20clients%20are%20interested%20in%2C%20identify%20what%20opportunities%20there%20are%2C%20and%20match%20that%20up%20with%20the%20clients'%20specific%20skills%20and%20backgrounds.%20It%20then%20creates%20a%20detailed%2C%20custom%20proposal%20that%20the%20client%20can%20use%20to%20try%20and%20secure%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDostiyarov%20said%20an%20average%20proposal%2C%20meaning%20the%20work%20put%20in%20before%20the%20consulting%20firm%20is%20even%20hired%20for%20a%20job%2C%20can%20take%2020%20hours%20of%20work%20or%20more%2C%20adding%20that%20with%20AI%20it%20can%20take%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDostiyarov%20used%20an%20analogy%20for%20their%20message%20to%20clients%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20find%20the%20house%20on%20fire%20for%20you%2C%20and%20then%20we%20are%20going%20to%20help%20you%20show%20up%20as%20the%20perfect%20firefighter%20for%20the%20job%20by%20giving%20you%20the%20perfect%20proposal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20all%20the%20data%20and%20all%20the%20capabilities%20that%20we%20have%20with%20our%20AI%2C%20we%20now%20can%20tell%20a%20perfect%20story%20as%20to%20why%20you%20are%20the%20great%20company%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20said%20Perceptis%20clients%20are%20often%20able%20to%20double%20or%20triple%20the%20number%20of%20proposals%20they%20send%20each%20month%20and%20experience%20higher%20conversation%20rates%20as%20well%20as%20increases%20in%20revenue%20soon%20after%20getting%20started%20with%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerceptis%20primarily%20serves%20small-%20to%20medium-sized%20firms%2C%20which%20typically%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20manpower%20as%20the%20biggest%20firms%20nor%20do%20they%20build%20their%20own%20internal%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20saw%20its%20biggest%20growth%20yet%20in%20November%20and%20December%2C%20doubling%20its%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%2C%20the%20cofounders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6d61592-fceb-4dcc-bddc-99f4fde108ca%5C%22%3EAI%20can't%20replace%20human%20consultants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Perceptis%20co-founders%20said%20they%20see%20AI%20as%20supplementing%20human%20consultants%2C%20not%20replacing%20them%2C%20and%20that%20the%20technology%20still%20has%20its%20limitations.%20They%20said%20AI%20can't%20replace%20human%20judgement%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now%2C%20or%20the%20human-to-human%20interaction%20that%20is%20needed%20in%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20think%20it%20could%20make%20the%20industry%20overall%20a%20lot%20more%20productive.%20AI%20could%20also%20potentially%20help%20smaller%20consultancies%20and%20even%20independent%20consultants%20compete%20more%20seriously%20in%20the%20space%20by%20taking%20over%20the%20tedious%20but%20necessary%20work%20that%20the%20bigger%20firms%20have%20more%20than%20enough%20employees%20to%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerceptis%20therefore%20democratizes%20access%20to%20consulting%20as%20an%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Dostiyarov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20they%20said%20the%20consulting%20industry%20could%20become%20a%20lot%20larger%2C%20more%20fragmented%2C%20and%20more%20specialized%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20the%20MBBs%20and%20Big%20Fours%20of%20the%20world%20could%20become%20a%20bit%20less%20dominant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20goliaths%20in%20the%20industry.%20We%20don't%20think%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20go%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Dostiyarov%20said.%20%26quot%3BStill%2C%20we%20think%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20growth%20is%20actually%20going%20to%20come%20from%20these%20much%20smaller%20firms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20consulting%20and%20have%20insights%20to%20share%20about%20the%20industry%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Akvlamis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ekvlamis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eor%20via%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal