et%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20one%20right-arm%20off-spinner%20in%20Washington%20Sundar.%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20returning%20to%20the%20Indian%20team%20after%20undergoing%20a%20sports%20hernia%20surgery%20in%20October%202024%2C%20is%20the%20lone%20wrist%20spinner%20in%20the%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20team%20management%20wanted%20Varun%20to%20bowl%20in%20ODI%20squad%20nets%20ahead%20of%20England%20series.%20Varun%20doesn't%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20domestic%20white%20ball%20season%20already%20concluded%2C%20he%20doesn't%20have%20any%20assignments%20till%20start%20of%20IPL%20end%20March.%20He%20is%20in%20good%20rhythm%20and%20they%20want%20him%20to%20continue%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20him%20being%20selected%20for%20the%20ODI%20series%20and%20subsequent%20Champions%20Trophy%20based%20on%20current%20form%2C%20the%20source%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20selectors%20have%20already%20picked%20four%20spinners%20and%20you%20only%20have%20three%20ODI%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20team%20management%20wants%20Varun%2C%20it%20will%20certainly%20have%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20chairman%20of%20selection%20committee.%20Whether%20they%20intend%20to%20or%20not%2C%20is%20still%20not%20known.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Men%20in%20Blue%20don't%20have%20a%20second%20wrist%20spinner%20and%20Chakravarthy's%20strong%20form%20could%20work%20in%20his%20favour.%20When%20he%20last%20played%20on%20the%20flatter%20tracks%20in%20Dubai%20during%20the%202021%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20Chakravarthy%20struggled%20to%20make%20an%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20has%20significantly%20improved%20since%20then%2C%20focusing%20more%20on%2