ink%20services%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A186%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-politics-starlink-expansion-complicated-south-africa-canada-trump-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGyan%20De%20Rahe%20Ho%3F%26quot%3B%20Speaker's%20Banter%20With%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETensions%20within%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20played%20out%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20as%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20criticised%20the%20BJP%20while%20distancing%20himself%20from%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20when%20he%20criticised%20the%20%26quot%3Binadequate%20attention%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20after%20the%201991%20economic%20reforms%2C%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20could%20not%20resist%20a%20quip%2C%20to%20which%20Mr%20Yadav%20replied%20his%20path%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bcycle%20track%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20tension%20along%20the%20China%20border%2C%20he%20said%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20opinions%20on%20the%20issue.%20Referring%20to%20the%20Congress%20era%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20one%20time%2C%20we%20lost%20lakhs%20of%20acres%20(to%20China).%20The%20BJP%20is%20now%20on%20the%20same%20path.%20But%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20even%20accept%20China%20has%20occupied.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav's%20remarks%20come%20a%20day%20after%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20Army%20has%20said%20Chinese%20are%20inside%20Indian%20territory.%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20has%20trashed%20the%20claim%20and%20said%20if%20India%20lost%20land%2C%20it%20was%20during%20the%201962%20conflict%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20reiterated%20his%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20survey%2C%20that%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20back%20this%20demand.%20%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20a%20caste%20survey%20to%20strengthen%20reservation.%20Now%20the%20Congress%20supports%20it%20too.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20not%20in%20support.%20If%20the%20Congress%20supported%20it%20then%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20ask%20for%20it%20now.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20my%20friends%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20that%20we%20are%20with%20you%20and%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20we%20will%20not%20just%20back%20you%20but%20take%20the%20lead.%20No%20one%20can%20stop%20a%20caste%20survey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20MPs%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%20claimed%20friction%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20friction%2C%20not%20like%20your%20double%20engine%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Mr%20Gandhi%20yesterday%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20spoke%20about%20China's%20growing%20influence%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20went%20back%20to%20history.%20Referring%20to%20the%201991%20economic%20reforms%20under%20the%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20government%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20our%20market%20was%20opened%2C%20economists%20understand%20this%20better%20than%20I%20do%2C%20but%20I%20understand%20that%20when%20our%20market%20was%20opened%2C%20adequate%20attention%20was%20not%20given%20to%20the%20economy.%20The%20manufacturing%20sector%20was%20not%20handled%20as%20responsibly%20as%20it%20should%20have%20been.%20If%20it%20was%2C%20probably%20we%20would%20have%20surged%20ahead%20of%20China.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20was%20significant%20because%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20economic%20reforms.%20As%20Mr%20Yadav%20continued%2C%20the%20Speaker%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you