%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20last%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20Last%20year%2C%20I%20was%20in%20discussions%20with%20managers%20about%20improving%20my%20performance%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20at%20risk%20of%20losing%20my%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20autism%2C%20I%20notice%20that%20my%20performance%20ebbs%20and%20changes%2C%20and%20I%20can%20get%20tired%20quickly.%20Sometimes%2C%20this%20is%20because%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.autism.org.uk%2Fadvice-and-guidance%2Fprofessional-practice%2Fautistic-burnout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eautistic%20burnout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20outside%20this%2C%20if%20I'm%20struggling%20with%20a%20problem%20and%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20get%20help%2C%20it%20quickly%20exhausts%20me.%20I%20worked%20with%20a%20psychiatrist%20to%20try%20to%20build%20up%20my%20capacity%2C%20which%20I%20think%20helped%20me%20to%20overcome%20some%20of%20my%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20struggle%20to%20understand%20some%20requests.%20Like%20when%20asked%20to%20%26quot%3Bpull%20something%20out%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20document%2C%20I%20wonder%20whether%20I'm%20meant%20to%20put%20that%20content%20in%20a%20new%20document%20or%20just%20remove%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20be%20very%20verbose%2C%20thinking%20that%20if%20I%20provide%20a%20lot%20of%20extra%20detail%20when%20communicating%2C%20I%20won't%20be%20misunderstood.%20However%2C%20this%20can%20be%20distracting%20for%20others.%20One%20manager%20suggested%20I%20write%20a%20TLDR%20above%20my%20message%2C%20which%20has%20been%20helpful%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259e44343-6e8f-4420-bf2f-61a855e4f459%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20neuro%20differences%20have%20also%20helped%20me%20stand%20out%20in%20positive%20ways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHyperfocus%20is%20one%20of%20the%20superpowers%20that%20comes%20with%20my%20neuro%20differences.%20Where%20other%20people%20