mortgages%2Fwhat-is-zillow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20data.%20This%20rate%20averaged%20around%206.71%25%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year%20fixed-rate%20mortgage%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20home%20loan.%20With%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Ftypes-of-mortgage-loans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etype%20of%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'll%20pay%20back%20what%20you%20borrowed%20over%2030%20years%2C%20and%20your%20interest%20rate%20won't%20change%20for%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lengthy%2030-year%20term%20allows%20you%20to%20spread%20out%20your%20payments%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20meaning%20you%20can%20keep%20your%20monthly%20payments%20lower%20and%20more%20manageable.%20The%20trade-off%20is%20that%20you'll%20have%20a%20higher%20rate%20than%20you%20would%20with%20shorter%20terms%2C%20like%20a%2015-year%20mortgage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b536fb75-9d34-4568-aba0-9db05d170f3e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%2215-Year%20Rates%5C%22%3E15-Year%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Today%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAverage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2F15-year-mortgage-rates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15-year%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20around%205.90%25%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow%20data.%20In%20January%2C%2015-year%20rates%20averaged%206.55%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20the%20predictability%20that%20comes%20with%20a%20fixed%20rate%20but%20are%20looking%20to%20spend%20less%20on%20interest%20over%20the%20life%20of%20your%20loan%2C%20a%2015-year%20fixed-rate%20mortgage%20might%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20you.%20Because%20these%20terms%20are%20shorter%20and%20have%20lower%20rates%20than%2030-year%20fixed-rate%20mortgages%2C%20you%20could%20potentially%20save%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20interest.%20However%2C%20you'll%20have%20a%20higher%20monthly%20payment%20than%20you%20would%20with%20a%20longer%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e67eca07-ac22-455e-8a0c-2c47721fceba%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Refinance%20Rates%5C%22%3EAverage%20Mortgage%20Refinance%20Rates%20Today%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERefinance%20rates%20are%20comparable%20to%20purchase%20rates%20at%20the%20moment.%20Last%20month%2C%2030-year%20refinance%20rates%20averaged%206.75%25%2C%20while%2015-year%20refinance%20rates%20were%20around%206.04%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222584473e-274c-4f8f-8419-b02349b15710%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20Much%20Do%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Need%20to%20Drop%20to%20Refinance%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20Much%20Do%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Need%20to%20Drop%20to%20Refinance%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20wondering%20if%20you%20should%20refinance%20now%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20crunch%20the%20numbers%20to%20see%20if%20it%20makes%20sense.%20Some%20experts%20advise%20only%20refinancing%20if%20you%20can%20reduce%20your%20rate%20by%20a%20percentage%20point%20or%20more%2C%20but%20it%20really%20comes%20down%20to%20whether%20it%20works%20for%20your%20individual%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can%20save%20enough%20each%20month%20by%20refinancing%20that%20you%20can%20recoup%20your%20costs%20in%20a%20reasonable%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20it%20might%20be%20worth%20it.%20You%20can%20calculate%20this%20by%20dividing%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwhat-are-mortgage-closing-costs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclosing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20amount%20you're%20saving%20on%20your%20monthly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Faverage-mortgage-payment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emortgage%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20paid%20%243%2C000%20to%20refinance%20and%20were%20able%20to%20lower%20your%20monthly%20payment%20by%20%24200%2C%20it%20would%20