and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fnq00d45o_exhibition_625x300_04_February_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20all%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20a%20Tasma%20Pah%3F%20Are%20we%20being%20dictated%20and%20conditioned%20by%20a%20sinister%20complex%2C%20a%20war%20machine%2C%20a%20capitalist%20cartel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20questions%20race%20through%20one's%20mind%20as%20one%20takes%20a%20walk%20through%20the%20dimly%20lit%20LTC%20gallery%20at%20Delhi's%20Bikaner%20House.%20Lights%20focused%20only%20on%20a%20clutch%20of%20paintings%20that%20are%20framed%20like%20innocuous%20mobile%20screens.%20You%20feel%20you%20are%20looking%20into%20your%20phone%20screens.%20The%20vivid%20images%20are%20all%20too%20familiar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20men%20wiling%20away%20their%20time%20at%20the%20tea%20stalls%2C%20at%20a%20%3Cem%3Emaidaan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20their%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20engrossed%20in%20their%20smartphones.%C2%A0%20Every%20painting%20has%20a%20foreground%20and%20a%20background.%20In%20the%20foreground%20are%20young%2C%20well-built%20men%20going%20about%20their%20usual%20business.%20The%20background%20is%20war%20scenes%2C%20destruction%2C%20drones%2C%20missiles%2C%20bombs%2C%20soldiers.%20The%20two%20are%20separate%20but%20together.%20The%20war%20is%20no%20more%20a%20bad%20thing.%20It's%20a%20spectacle%20that's%20beamed%20live%20into%20our%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20on%20our%20cellphones%2C%20making%20us%20numb%20and%20immune%20to%20its%20horrors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20like%20a%20mobile%20game%20where%20friends%20take%20pleasure%20in%20killing%20each%20other.%20Robots%20and%20fictional%20figures%20blow%20each%20other%20up%20on%20phone%20screens.%20Blowing%20up%20humans%2C%20razing%20houses%2C%20bombing%20schools%2C%20all%20look%20the%20same%20on%20the%20evil%20screen.%20Who%20has%20the%20time%20or%20attention%20to%20be%20shocked%20or%20to%20mourn%3F%20It's%20all%20just%2015-second%20content.%20The%20next%20reel%20or%20the%20next%20image%20will%20demand%20a%20different%20reaction%20or%20emotion.%20Digital%20decadence%20at%20its%20worst.%20Men%20are%20machines.%20Humans%20are%20just%20metadata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F40ads0do_exhibition_625x300_04_February_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrones%20hover%20like%20demons%20in%20the%20paintings.%20The%20joystick%20that%20controls%20the%20drone%20is%20the%20modern-day%20arrow%20in%20the%20quiver%20of%20Paris%20(In%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Iliad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Paris%20is%20responsible%20for%20starting%20the%20Trojan%20War).%20Modern%20day%20Paris%20can%20make%20a%20quick%20killing%20even%20on%20a%20holiday.%20The%20war%20machine%20has%20got%20a%20new%20toy.%20The%20drone%20can%20kill%20a%20%26quot%3Btarget%26quot%3B%20miles%20away.%20The%20killer%20sees%20the%20action%20on%20a%20small%20screen.%20Humans%20become%20shadowy%20figures%20on%20the%20screen.%20The%20targets.%20Click%2C%20boom%2C%20gone.%20Game%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20work%2C%20a%20young%20soldier%20gleefully%20posts%20a%20selfie%20from%20the%20warzone%20strutting%20on%20a%20little%20girl's%20bike.%20He%20tags%20a%20caption%3A%20'Mother%2C%20you%20would%20be%20proud.%20Killing%20is%20fun'.%20The%20image%20appears%20on%20millions%20of%20phones.%20Killing%20becomes%20normal.%20No%20one%20is%20shocked%20anymore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20ago%2C%20the%20image%20of%20Aylan%20Kurdi%20washing%20ashore%20lifeless%20shocked%20the%20world.%20Now%2C%20dead%20and%20bleeding%20children%20are%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20paintings%2C%20the%20soldiers%20are%20depicted%20with%20their%20necks%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20Tasma%20Pah.%20The%20ordinary%20men%20are%20all%20beefed%20up%2C%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20gym.%20Flaunting%20their%20biceps%20and%20abs%20in%20tight%20tees.%20Probably%2C%20their%20bodies%20are%20the%20only%20thing%20they%20control%2C%20and%20which%20give%20them%20a%20sense%20of%20achievement.%20There%20is%20pressure%20on%20everyone%20to%20look%20the%20type.%20And%20cracking%20it%20makes%20these%20young%20men%20feel%20they%20have%20arrived.%20That%20they%20belong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELies.%20Big%20lies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELie%20Machine%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20exhibition%20by%20Moonis%20Ijlal%2C%20is%20haunting%20and%20disturbing.%20We%20just%20watch.%20We%20don't%20speak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20do%20not%20even%20have%20the%20language%20to%20say%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20you%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20these%20words%20scream%20at%20you%20at%20the%20gallery%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Felr3unf8_exhibition_625x300_04_February_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20genesis%20of%20these%20images%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIjlal%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BLie%20machine%20began%20with%20a%20post-midnight%20routine%20of%20stepping%20out%20for%20chai%20with%20my%20cousins%20and%20their%20friends.%20I%20saw%20a%20world%20is%20awake%20after%20dark%20of%20young%20men%20and%20women%20making%20reels%20on%20their%20phones%2C%20at%20times%20dangerously%2C%20on%20the%20side%20of%20flyovers%20with%20speeding%20trucks%20and%20cars%20whizzing%20past%20them.%20At%20the%3Cem%3E%20chai%20dhabas%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Estudent%20gamers%20played%20%3Cem%3E