%20frankly%20and%20nonjudgmentally%20about%20the%20role%20of%20mind-altering%20substances%20in%20people's%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20legal%20and%20illegal%2C%20good%20and%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20difference%20between%20normalizing%20drug%20use%20that's%20healthy%20and%20normalizing%20drug%20use%20that's%20problematic%2C%26quot%3B%20Hashemi%20told%20me.%20As%20she%20sees%20it%2C%20that%20distinction%20depends%20on%20the%20role%20that%20a%20particular%20substance%20is%20playing%20in%20a%20person's%20life%20at%20any%20given%20time.%20A%20healthy%20adult%20life%20revolves%20around%20competing%20priorities%3A%20romantic%20relationships%2C%20social%20relationships%2C%20a%20career%2C%20and%20physical%20and%20mental%20health.%20Healthy%20drug%20use%20happens%20in%20harmony%20with%20the%20bigger%20picture.%20It's%20the%20pinch%20of%20a%20certain%20something%20that%20helps%20make%20memories%20with%20friends%20without%20becoming%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20relationship%2C%20or%20that%20washes%20away%20the%20residues%20of%20a%20tough%20week%20at%20work%20without%20becoming%20a%20contingency%20plan%20for%20getting%20through%20the%20next%20one.%20It's%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20honest%20and%20step%20away%20if%20and%20when%20drugs%20begin%20disrupting%20the%20balance%20between%20everything%20else%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20into%20a%20need%20instead%20of%20an%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHashemi%20said%20it's%20also%20critical%20to%20emphasize%20that%20different%20substances%20carry%20far%20greater%20potential%20for%20harm%20to%20the%20still%20developing%20brain%20of%20a%20person%20in%20their%20teens%20or%20early%2020s%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20difference%20between%20a%20parent%20using%20cannabis%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20%E2%80%94%20or%20psychedelics%20or%20MDMA%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20child.%20These%20are%20all%20nuances%20that%20should%20be%20very%20explicit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20talk%20is%20still%20a%20few%20years%20away%20for%20Katie%2C%20th