%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20words%20attributed%20to%20the%20Army%20Chief%20by%20Shri%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20were%20never%20spoken%20by%20him%20at%20any%20time.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20deep%20regret%20that%20Shri%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20indulge%20in%20irresponsible%20politics%20on%20matters%20of%20national%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20territory%20lost%20during%20the%201962%20Sino-Indian%20conflict%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20at%20all%20there%20is%20Indian%20Territory%20into%20which%20China%20has%20come%2C%20this%20is%2038%2C000%20sq.%20km%20in%20Aksai%20Chin%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%201962%20conflict%20and%205%2C180%20sq.%20km.%20illegally%20ceded%20by%20Pakistan%20to%20China%20in%201963.%20Shri%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20may%20consider%20introspecting%20about%20this%20phase%20of%20our%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interaction%20with%20the%20media%20last%20month%2C%20General%20Dwivedi%20had%20said%20India%20and%20China%20are%20still%20locked%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdegree%20of%20standoff%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20Army%20is%20looking%20at%20diplomatic%20negotiations%20to%20resolve%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20status%20of%20standoff%20(with%20China)%20is%20concerned...we%20have%20to%20see%20what%20all%20has%20changed%20since%20April%202020.%20Has%20the%20terrain%20been%20doctored%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%3F%20Yes%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20doctored%20the%20terrain.%20Have%20both%20sides%20carried%20out%20constructions%3F%20Yes.%20Both%20sides%20have%20carried%20out%20some%20stocking%2C%20deployment%3F%20Yes.%20Therefore%2C%20what%20it%20means%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20degree%20of%20standoff%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20Dwivedi%20said.%C2%A0The%20Army%20Chief%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20the%20two%20sides%20to%20sit%20together%20and%20come%20to%20a%20broader