w.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20stepped%20up%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-warehouse-robots-expansion-proteus-hercules-jobs-workers-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erobotics%20development%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20it%20could%20save%20the%20e-commerce%20giant%20as%20much%20as%20%2410%20billion%20annually%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20a%20research%20note%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20fleet%20of%20more%20than%20750%2C000%20robots%20now%20works%20across%20every%20part%20of%20the%20fulfillment%20process.%20They%20help%20with%20storage%20and%20inventory%20management%2C%20picking%2C%20packing%2C%20and%20sorting%2C%20and%20they%20transport%20packages%20to%20the%20fulfillment%20center's%20loading%20dock%2C%20where%20they%20are%20then%20sent%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202022%20Amazon%20has%20introduced%20six%20new%20models.%20They%20include%20a%20fully%20autonomous%20mobile%20robot%20called%20Proteus%2C%20three%20types%20of%20robotic%20arms%2C%20and%20a%20containerized%20storage%20system%20called%20Sequoia.%20Amazon%20also%20has%20robots%20that%20can%20create%20custom%20packaging%20based%20on%20an%20item's%20specific%20dimensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20opened%20its%20first%20%26quot%3Bnext-generation%26quot%3B%20fulfillment%20center%2C%20incorporating%20all%20of%20its%20latest%20robots%2C%20in%20Shreveport%2C%20Louisiana%2C%20in%20September.%20The%20company%20has%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20see%20a%2025%25%20improvement%20in%20fulfillment%20costs%20during%20peak%20periods%20at%20the%20Shreveport%20warehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20estimated%20that%20if%2030%25%20to%2040%25%20of%20Amazon%20orders%20in%20the%20US%20were%20fulfilled%20through%20next-gen%20warehouses%20by%202030%2C%20the%20company%20could%20save%20as%20much%20as%20%2410%20billion%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20noted%2C%20however%2C%20that%20fully%20scaling%20robotics%20would%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20ahead%2C%20we%20expect%20AMZN%20to%20continue%20to%20expand%20its%20warehouse%20network%20(to%20support%20growth)%20while%20also%20upgrading%20the%20footprint%20toward%20next-gen%20robotics%20in%20new%20builds%20and%20retrofits%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20question%20of%20how%20quickly%20Amazon%20shifts%20volumes%20to%20robotics%20enabled%20warehouses%20will%20likely%20come%20down%20to%20reasonable%20and%20improving%20paces%20of%20build%2Fretrofit%20(current%20new%20robotics%20plants%20still%20take%201-2%20years)%20balanced%20with%20not%20wanting%20to%20cause%20near-term%20disruption%20to%20AMZN's%20retail%20service.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext-gen%20fulfillment%20centers%20are%20significantly%20more%20expensive%20to%20develop%20than%20Amazon's%20traditional%20fulfillment%20centers.%20The%20analysts%20cited%20news%20reports%20that%20say%20the%20robotic-powered%20warehouses%20cost%20about%20%24450%20million%20to%20develop%2C%20compared%20with%20%24200%20million%20for%20traditional%20development%20and%20%24100%20million%20to%20retrofit%20an%20older%20warehouse%20with%20robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20estimate%20AMZN%20will%20have%20%2460bn%20of%20net%20cash%20as%20of%20year-end%20'24%20and%20will%20generate%20~%24150bn%20of%20aggregate%20free%20cash%20flow%20in%20'25%2F'26%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAs%20such%2C%20investment%20capital%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20a%20constraint%20to%20how%20quickly%20AMZN%20shifts%20to%20next-gen%20robotics...which%20means%20if%20they%20can%20build%20and%20shift%20without%20service%20disruption%20they%20likely%20will%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%20also%20said%20that%20if%20Amazon%20invested%20further%20in%20bringing%20robots%20to%20sorting%20centers%20and%20in%20scaling%20the%20technology%20internationally%2C%20it%20could%20see%20more%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-robots-could-save-10-billion-a-year-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738663202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a13ed5bfebcc4d029da17c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-robots-could-save-10-billion-a-year-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon%20has%20introduced%20six%20new%20types%20of%20robots%20since%202022.%20They%20could%20save%20the%20company%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mstone%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Stone)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-robots-could-save-10-billion-a-year-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20Ohio%20data%20center%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20natural%20gas%20plant%20as%20the%20AI%20boom%20creates%20an%20electricity%20strain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20Albany%2C%20OH%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5617e636bd86ef175c8b58c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22639%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20Albany%2C%20a%20rural%20suburb%20northeast%20of%20Columbus%2C%20Ohio%2C%20has%20become%20a%20fast-growing%20market%20for%20data%20centers%20and%20could%20soon%20be%20home%20to%20a%20natural%20gas-fired%20power%20plant.%3Cp%3EFacebook%2FNew%20Albany%2C%20Ohio%20Government%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPowerconnex%20notified%20state%20regulators%20of%20plans%20for%20a%20120%20MW%20natural%20gas%20plant%20in%20New%20Albany.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20plant%20would%20serve%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20electricity%20for%20a%20data%20center%20on%20the%20same%20site.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20energy%20demand%20from%20AI%20strains%20the%2