nd%20in%20the%20region%20has%20soared.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faep-ohio-data-centers-pay-for-electricity-demand-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAEP%20Ohio%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Columbus%20utility%20that%20serves%20the%20major%20data%20centers%2C%20said%20last%20year%20that%20it%20had%20received%2030%20gigawatts%20of%20service%20requests.%20It%20asked%20state%20regulators%20to%20approve%20a%20separate%20rate%20class%20specifically%20for%20data%20center%20customers%20to%20protect%20other%20ratepayers%20from%20incurring%20additional%20costs%20due%20to%20the%20facilities'%20demand.%C2%A0Hearings%20for%20the%20matter%20were%20held%20in%20January%2C%20although%20the%20Public%20Utilities%20Commission%20of%20Ohio%20has%20not%20yet%20issued%20a%20final%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20or%20have%20knowledge%20of%20the%20data%20center%20industry%20and%20have%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aethomas%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eethomas%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20reach%20out%20via%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20%2B1-929-524-6924.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnatural-gas-to-power-new-albany-data-center-filing-shows-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738663202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a144687bb3f854015b9bea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnatural-gas-to-power-new-albany-data-center-filing-shows-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Developers%20for%20Powerconnex%20have%20notified%20Ohio%20regulators%20of%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20120%20MW%20natural%20gas%20plan