importing%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20client%20note%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsp500-returns-outlook-decade-flat-returns-mike-wilson-morgan-stanley-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMike%20Wilson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bank's%20chief%20investment%20officer%20and%20top%20US%20equity%20strategist%2C%20said%20that%20his%20team%20is%20partial%20to%20services-oriented%20areas%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTariffs%20reinforce%20our%20preference%20for%20services%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20wrote%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20expect%20the%20market%20to%20rotate%20further%20toward%20services%20given%20recent%20trade%20policy%20implementation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20highlighted%20four%20services%20sectors%20he's%20particularly%20bullish%20on%3A%20%3Cstrong%3Esoftware%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Efinancials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Econsumer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eservices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Emedia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eentertainment%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20came%20as%20US%20stock%20indexes%20plummeted%20on%20Monday%20after%20President%20Trump's%20tariffs%20went%20into%20effect%20over%20the%20weekend.%20Trump%20initially%20announced%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20all%20goods%20imported%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20and%2010%25%20tariffs%20on%20goods%20from%20China.%20But%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-mexico-delayed-month-sheinbaum-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etemporarily%20paused%20his%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20when%20the%20country%20said%20it%20would%20send%2010%2C000%20troops%20to%20its%20border%20with%20the%20US%20to%20help%20slow%20illegal%20crossings.%20A%20similar%20pause%20was%20reached%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrudeau-trump-tariffs-canadian-goods-paused-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanada%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Trump%20has%20also%20threatened%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20the%20European%20Union%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Wilson's%20favoring%20of%20services%20stocks%20goes%20beyond%20tariffs.%20He%20said%20services%20industries%20would%20see%20the%20largest%20efficiency%20increases%20thanks%20to%20AI%2C%20something%20that%20is%20already%20showing%20up%20in%20performance.%20The%20median%20stock%20among%20AI%20adopters%20in%20the%20services%20industries%20is%20up%202024%20over%20the%20last%2013%20months%2C%20compared%20to%209%25%20for%20the%20median%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20stock.%20Even%20including%20non-AI%20adopters%2C%20the%20median%20services%20industries%20stock%20is%20up%2017%25%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20structural%20tailwind%20strengthens%20the%20case%20for%20favoring%20services%20industries%20beyond%20the%20cyclical%20drivers%20that%20are%20supporting%20these%20pockets%20of%20the%20market%20(stronger%20pricing%20power%2C%20stronger%20earnings%20revisions%20and%20more%20limited%20tariff%20headwinds)%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20further%20recent%20positive%20catalyst%20for%20AI%20adopters%20is%20DeepSeek's%20R1%20chatbot%2C%20which%20came%20out%20in%20late%20January.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOptimizing%20GenAI%20models%20is%20not%20a%20new%20phenomenon%2C%20but%20what%20this%20news%20cycle%20appeared%20to%20do%20is%20turn%20investors'%20focus%20toward%20the%20idea%20that%20cheaper%20models%20are%20likely%20to%20increase%20adoption%20and%20drive%20efficiencies%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20it%20drew%20market%20participants'%20attention%20to%20the%20significant%20value%20in%20the%20application%20layer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoftware%20and%20media%20and%20entertainment%20are%20particularly%20well-positioned%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20adoption%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp