%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-tariffs-trump-canada-mexico-trade-war-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%20on%20a%20range%20of%20US%20goods%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20coal%2C%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%2C%20crude%20oil%2C%20and%20agricultural%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US's%20unilateral%20imposition%20of%20tariffs%20seriously%20violates%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%2C%26quot%3B%20China's%20Finance%20Ministry%20said%20in%20its%20tariffs%20announcement.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20only%20unhelpful%20in%20solving%20its%20own%20problems%2C%20but%20also%20undermines%20the%20normal%20economic%20and%20trade%20cooperation%20between%20China%20and%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20said%20fentanyl%20is%20the%20US'%20own%20problem%20and%20that%20Beijing%20would%20challenge%20the%20tariffs%20at%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20needs%20to%20view%20and%20solve%20its%20own%20fentanyl%20issue%20in%20an%20objective%20and%20rational%20way%20instead%20of%20threatening%20other%20countries%20with%20arbitrary%20tariff%20hikes%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxw%2Ffyrbt%2F202502%2Ft20250202_11548196.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20foreign%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20taking%20the%20same%20brinkmanship%20approach%20to%20China%2C%20said%20Alex%20Capri%2C%20an%20international%20trade%20specialist%20and%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore's%20business%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20will%20take%20the%20same%20approach%20to%20China%20and%20I%20think%20Beijing%20will%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20welcome%20this%20transactional%20way%20of%20doing%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Capri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F