%20you%20feel%20about%20money%3F%20How%20do%20you%20want%20to%20feel%20about%20money%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ask%20them%20to%20pull%20out%20their%20notebooks%20and%20do%20two%20to%20three%20minutes%20of%20independent%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answers%20to%20the%20first%20prompt%20represent%20their%20starting%20point.%20Everyone%20has%20a%20different%20starting%20point%20%E2%80%94%20we%20all%20come%20from%20different%20financial%20backgrounds%20%E2%80%94%20but%20where%20they%20start%20from%20really%20isn't%20all%20that%20important.%20What%20matters%20is%20that%20they%20have%20some%20level%20of%20control%20over%20their%20trajectory%2C%20and%20they%20get%20from%20what%20they%20wrote%20down%20for%20prompt%20No.%201%20to%20what%20they%20wrote%20down%20for%20prompt%20No.%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20we%20get%20into%20two%20components%20of%20personal%20finance%20that%20can%20impact%20trajectory%3A%20Saving%20%E2%80%94%20how%20to%20keep%20a%20portion%20of%20your%20income%20%E2%80%94%20and%20investing%2C%20which%20is%20the%20key%20to%20building%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20acknowledge%20the%20importance%20of%20paying%20yourself%20first.%20When%20they%20ask%20how%20much%2C%20I%20point%20to%20the%2050%2F30%2F20%20rule%20of%20thumb%2C%20which%20suggests%20putting%2050%25%20of%20your%20income%20toward%20needs%2C%2030%25%20toward%20wants%2C%20and%2020%25%20toward%20savings.%20I%20emphasize%20that%20starting%20with%20a%20small%20savings%20rate%20of%20even%20just%201%25%20is%20better%20than%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20students%20are%20familiar%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20budgeting%2C%20even%20if%20they%20don't%20actively%20budget.%20I%20challenge%20them%20to%20think%20about%20budgeting%20not%20as%20restrictive%2C%20as%20it's%20often%20portrayed%2C%20but%20as%20liberating.%20If%20they%20successfully%20divvy%20up%20their%20paycheck%20according%20to%20the%2050%2F30%2F20%20rule%2C%20for%20example%2C%20they%20have%2030%25%20of%20their%20income%20to%20spend%20on%20whatever%20fills%20their%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20two%20is%20all%20about%20growing%20your%20savings%20by%20putting%20it%20to%20work%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20compound%20interest%2C%20and%20understanding%20that%20time%20is%20on%20your%20side%20as%20a%20young%20investor.%20Every%20year%2C%20without%20fail%2C%20this%20is%20the%20moment%20when%20the%20energy%20in%20the%20room%20shifts.%20Ears%20perk.%20Hands%20shoot%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20I'm%20reminded%20that%20young%20people%20are%20fascinated%20by%20the%20concept%20of%20investing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20data%20shows%20this%20generation%20is%20curious%20enough%20to%20take%20action%3A%20Gen%20Z%20started%20investing%20at%20a%20much%20earlier%20age%20on%20average%2C%2019%2C%20than%20baby%20boomers%20(35)%20and%20millennials%20(25)%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frpc.cfainstitute.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fdocuments%2Farticle%2Findustry-research%2FGen_Z_and_Investing.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Schwab%20Modern%20Wealth%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20my%20students%20don't%20fully%20understand%20how%20compounding%20works%20or%20how%20it%20relates%20to%20an%20investment%20account.%20They're%20smart%20kids%2C%20but%20chances%20are%20that%20they%20didn't%20engage%20with%20this%20material%20in%20high%20school%3A%20In%202022%2C%20just%2023%25%20of%20high%20school%20students%20in%20the%20US%20were%20required%20to%20take%20a%20personal%20finance%20class%2C%20up%20from%2016%25%20in%202018%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd3f7q2msm2165u.cloudfront.net%2Faaa-content%2Fuser%2Ffiles%2FFiles%2FNGPFAnnualReport_2022.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20research%20from%20Next%20Gen%20Personal%20Finance.%3C%2Fa%3E%20That%20percentage%20has%20continued%20to%20increase%3A%20As%20of%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.councilforeconed.org%2Ffinancial-education-requirements-soar-in-americas-high-schools%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520the%2520Council%2520for%2Cthe%2520states%2520had%2520such%2520mandates.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20all%20states%20require%20personal%20finance%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20high%20school%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20analyze%20compound%20interest%20charts%20that%20show%20just%20how%20much%20of%20an%20edge%20they%20have%20simply%20by%20starting%20young%2C%20including%20this%20one%20from%20the%20St.%20Louis%20Fed%20comparing%20an%20investor%20who%20starts%20at%2025%20and%20another%20who%20starts%20at%2035.%20The%20one%20who%20starts%20early%20ends%20up%20with%20a%20significantly%20bigger%20portfolio%2C%20even%20though%20they%20invest%20for%2020%20fewer%20years%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethan%20the%20investor%20who%20started%20at%2035.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22865%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22compound%20interest%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d667aeb4be2fff9a32dd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22887%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20St.%20Louis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20plug%20numbers%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investor.gov%2Ffinancial-tools-calculators%2Fcalculators%2Fcompound-interest-calculator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20compound%20interest%20calculator%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20figure%20out%20how%20much%20money%20they'd%20have%20to%20save%20a%20month%20to%20become%20millionaires%20by%2050.%20It's%20often%20less%20than%20they%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tricky%20lesson%20to%20convey%20is%20how%20to%20actually%20take%20advantage%20of%20compounding%3A%20How%20to%20start%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20significant%20lack%20of%20understanding.%20The%20common%20misconceptions%20I've%20picked%20up%20on%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInvesting%20is%20for%20rich%20people%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvesting%20is%20for%20people%20who%20know%20a%20lot%20about%20finance%20and%20economics%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvesting%20means%20buying%20individual%20stocks%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvesting%20is%20risky%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20discuss%20passive%20investing%20strategies%20and%20how%20anyone%20can%20invest%20in%20funds%20that%20track%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20with%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20money%2C%20I%20can%20sense%20the%20eagerness%20and%20excitement%20as%20the%20students%20start%20to%20understand%20that%20they%20can%20actually%20participate%20%E2%80%94%20that%20investing%20isn't%20just%20for%20rich%20people%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20they%20can%20contribute%20starting%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20reminded%20every%20year%20I%20step%20into%20the%20classroom%20that%20there's%20an%20appetite%20for%20financial%20literacy.%20We%20just%20need%20to%20keep%20talking%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-personal-finance-lessons-for-young-people-compound-interest-investing-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738661402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d5de7bfebcc4d029d7293%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-personal-finance-lessons-for-young-people-compound-interest-investing-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I'm%20reminded%20every%20year%20I%20step%20into%20the%20classroom%20that%20there's%20an%20appetite%20for%20financial%20literacy.%20We%20just%20need%20to%20keep%20talking%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-personal-finance-lessons-for-young-people-compound-interest-investing-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Virgin%20of%20the%20Quarry%20Lake%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Adolescent%20Envy%20Turns%20Deadly%20in%20an%20Atmospheric%20Argentine%20Oddity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738661325000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FThe-Virgin-of-Quarry-Lake.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236295119%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whatever%20summer%20temperature%20it%20is%20where%20the%20average%20person%E2%80%99s%20mind%20begins%20to%20warp%20and%20melt%20in%20the%20general%20heat-haze%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Virgin%20of%20the%20Quarry%20Lake%E2%80%9D%20is%20set%20permanently%20to%20that%20exact%20degree.%20You%20can%20feel%20the%20slow%2C%20sweaty%20adhesion%20of%20skin%20to%20every%20surface%20%E2%80%94%20or%20simply%20to%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Argentine%20director%20Laura%20Casab%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guy%20Lodge%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Fthe-virgin-of-the-quarry-lake-review-1236295119%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hidden%20Mud%20Volcano%20Under%20The%20Arctic%20Ocean%20Full%20Of%20Life%2C%20Say%20Scientists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20mud%20volcano%2C%20deep%20beneath%20the%20icy%20waters%20of%20the%20Barents%20Sea%2C%20is%20flourishing%20with%20marine%20life%2C%20scientists%20have%20confirmed.%20The%20Borealis%20Mud%20Volcano%2C%20400%20metres%20below%20the%20surface%2C%20continuously%20releases%20methane-rich%20fluids%2C%20creating%20a%20unique%20deep-sea%20ecosystem%20that%20researchers%20now%20believe%20serves%20as%20a%20sanctuary%20for%20vulnerable%20species.%20The%20Barents%20Sea%20is%20in%20the%20Arctic%20Ocean%2C%20north%20of%20Norway%20and%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Borealis%20Mud%20Volcano%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fdirect-window-into-earth-underwater-volcano-discovered-in-barents-sea-4081270%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscovered%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20scientists%20from%20UiT%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Arctic%20University%20of%20Norway%20using%20a%20remotely%20operated%20vehicle%20(ROV)%20called%20Aurora.%20The%20ROV%20captured%20high-resolution%20footage%20and%20collected%20samples%2C%20showing%20the%20seafloor%20around%20the%20volcano%20covered%20with%20carbonate%20deposits.%20This%20suggests%20that%20methane%20has%20been%20seeping%20from%20the%20site%20for%20thousands%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20regular%20volcanoes%20that%20erupt%20with%20lava%2C%20mud%20volcanoes%20release%20mud%2C%20gases%2C%20and%20water%20from%20beneath%20the%20Earth's%20crust.%20The%20methane-rich%20environment%20at%20Borealis%20has%20created%20a%20unique%20ecosystem%20where%20marine%20life%20has%20adapted%20and%20is%20thriving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20extreme%20environment%2C%20the%20Borealis%20Mud%20Volcano%20is%20teeming%20with%20life.%20ROV%20footage%20and%20samples%20revealed%20a%20variety%20of%20marine%20creatures%2C%20including%20anemones%2C%20tube-dwelling%20worms%20called%20serpulidae%2C%20sea%20slugs%20(nudibranchs)%2C%20and%20small%20hydroid%20colonies%20clinging%20to%20the%20volcano's%20crust.%20Sparse%20octocoral%20colonies%2C%20which%20usually%20thrive%20in%20deep-sea%20habitats%2C%20were%20also%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20carbonate%20formations%20around%20the%20volcano%20serve%20as%20both%20a%20habitat%20and%20a%20refuge%20from%20bottom%20trawling%2C%20offering%20feeding%20grounds%20for%20fish.%20Scientists%20recorded%20large%20schools%20of%20saithe%2C%20spotted%20wolffish%2C%20and%20various%20redfish%20species%2C%20including%20the%20endangered%20Atlantic%20redfish%2C%20which%20has%20been%20severely%20overfished%20and%20is%20currently%20protected%20under%20a%20fishing%20moratorium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20findings%20were%20positive.%20Researchers%20also%20spotted%20abandoned%20fishing%20gear%20tangled%20around%20the%20jagged%20carbonate%20rocks%2C%20evidence%20of%20human%20activity%20encroaching%20on%20this%20fragile%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBorealis%20is%20an%20oasis%20where%20different%20species%20can%20thrive%20and%20flourish%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurekalert.org%2Fnews-releases%2F1071753%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20study%20lead%20author%3C%2Fa%3E%20Giuliana%20Panieri%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20UiT%20The%20Arctic%20University%20of%20Norway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20are%20calling%20the%20Borealis%20Mud%20Volcano%20a%20%E2%80%9Cde%20facto%20sanctuary%E2%80%9D%20for%20endangered%20species%2C%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20conservation%20efforts.%20Preserving%20this%20unique%20ecosystem%2C%20they%20argue%2C%20is%20crucial%20for%20maintaining%20marine%20biodiversity%20and%20understanding%20how%20geology%2C%20geochemistry%2C%20and%20biology%20interact%20in%20deep-sea%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20has%20broader%20implications%20for%20oceanic%20research.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Arctic%20seabed%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%20extraction%20activities%20and%20the%20emerging%20deep-sea%20mining%20industry%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Panieri%20noted.%20Studying%20natural%20methane%20emissions%20like%20those%20from%20the%20Borealis%20Mud%20Volcano%20can%20also%20provide%20insights%20into%20climate%20regulation%2C%20as%20methane%20is%20a%20potent%20greenhouse%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738660860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F6s8de5g_underwater-volcano-borealis-1200_625x300_31_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhidden-mud-volcano-under-the-arctic-ocean-full-of-life-say-scientists-7630766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Borealis%20Mud%20V