ing%20for%20the%20family%20to%20build%20a%20trust%20and%20land%20will%20be%20allocated%20once%20it's%20formed%2C%20sources%20said.%20The%20government%20will%20provide%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20the%20trust%20to%20build%20the%20memorial%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20is%20known%20for%20leaving%20a%20lasting%20impact%20on%20the%20country's%20economic%20landscape.%20He%20was%20the%20finance%20minister%20in%201991%20when%20India%20witnessed%20groundbreaking%20reforms%20that%20opened%20the%20country's%20economy%20to%20the%20world.%20He%20served%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20during%202004-2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20death%20on%20December%2026%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Congress%20slammed%20the%20government%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20find%20a%20suitable%20location%20for%20Mr%20Singh's%20memorial.%20Hitting%20back%2C%20the%20BJP%20reminded%20the%20Congress%20that%20it%20never%20built%20a%20memorial%20for%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20controversy%20raged%2C%20the%20government%20last%20month%20allocated%20land%20for%20the%20memorial%20of%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20died%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20earmarked%20a%20plot%20in%20the%20'Rashtriya%20Samiti'%20complex%20in%20the%20Rajghat%20precinct%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20former%20president's%20daughter%20said%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalled%20on%20Hon'ble%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%20to%20express%20thanks%20and%20gratitude%20from%20the%20core%20of%20my%20heart%20for%20his%20government's%20decision%20to%20create%20a%20memorial%20for%20baba.%20It's%20more%20cherished%20considering%20that%20we%20didn't%20ask%20for%20it.%20Immensely%20touched%20by%20this%20unexpected%20but%20truly%20gracious%20gesture%20by%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharmistha%20Mukherjee%20said%20in%20an%20online%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mukherjee%20had%20even%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20its%20demand%20for%20Mr%20Singh's%20memorial%20and%20reminded%20them%20they%20did%20not%20even%20convene%20a%20condolence%20meeting%20for%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738657200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fdf8abgq8_pranab-mukherjee-manmohan-singh_625x300_07_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanmohan-singhs-memorial-may-come-up-next-to-pranab-mukherjee-sources-7630723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20centre%20has%20offered%20land%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20family%20in%20the%20Rajghat%20complex%20to%20build%20a%20memorial%20for%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20who%20died%20in%20December%2C%20government%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanmohan-singhs-memorial-may-come-up-next-to-pranab-mukherjee-sources-7630723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEngines%20Colliding%3F%26quot%3B%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20Uses%20BJP%20Slogan%20To%20Jab%20Yogi%20Adityanath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThose%20claiming%20to%20have%20organised%20a%20digital%20Kumbh%20could%20not%20give%20digits%20to%20the%20casualties%20in%20the%20Prayagraj%20stampede%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20as%20he%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20House%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President's%20address%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20the%20Centre%20had%20quoted%20big%20numbers%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget.%20%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20a%20lot%20of%20numbers%20in%20the%20Budget%2C%20they%20should%20also%20give%20the%20numbers%20of%20the%20dead%20at%20Mahakumbh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETragedy%20struck%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Ganga%20at%20Prayagraj%20when%20the%20rush%20for%20a%20holy%20dip%20led%20to%20a%20stampede%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20January%2029.%20After%20the%20administration's%20long%20silence%20over%20the%20number%20of%20casualties%2C%20police%20eventually%20put%20the%20number%20at%2030%20dead%20and%2060%20injured.%20Critics%20have%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20actual%20figure%20is%20much%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemanding%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20Mahakumbh%20tragedy%20and%20arrangements%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20demanded%20that%20a%20report%20on%20the%20casualties%20and%20arrangements%20be%20submitted%20in%20Parliament.%20%26quot%3BThose%20hiding%20the%20truth%20be%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20question%20the%20double-engine%20government.%20If%20there%20is%20no%20guilty%20conscience%2C%20why%20were%20numbers%20suppressed%20and%20hidden%3F%20Hiding%20the%20truth%20is%20a%20crime.%20Who%20will%20serve%20the%20punishment%20for%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20said%20the%20focus%20during%20the%20religious%20congregation%20was%20on%20publicity%20and%20not%20arrangements.%20A%20government's%20publicity%20at%20a%20religious%20gathering%20is%20condemnable%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20claiming%20to%20have%20organised%20a%20Digital%20Kumbh%20could%20not%20give%20the%20digits%20of%20those%20killed%20(in%20the%20stampede).%20Someone%20lost%20parents%2C%20someone%20a%20daughter%2C%20someone%20siblings.%20The%20figure%20of%20children%20is%20still%20missing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20asked%20saints%20to%20cancel%20the%20shahi%20snan%20and%20broke%20an%20age-old%20tradition.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20matter%20was%20raised%2C%20they%20ordered%20the%20akharas%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20shahi%20snan.%20They%20broke%20the%20sanatan%20tradition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20came%20for%20'punya'%20returned%20with%20the%20bodies%20of%20their%20near%20and%20dear%20ones%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDevotees'%20bodies%20had%20been%20found%2C%20but%20the%20government%20was%20not%20admitting%20deaths.%20When%20it%20was%20known%20that%20people%20had%20died%2C%20the%20government%20loaded%20a%20helicopter%20with%20flowers%20and%20dropped%20them.%20Which%20tradition%20is%20this%3F%20There%20were%20slippers%2C%20sarees.%20They%20were%20scraped%20up%20with%20earth%20movers%2C%20no%20one%20knows%20where%20they%20were%20thrown%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20direct%20attack%20on%20Mr%20Adityanath%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20did%20not%20express%20grief%20over%20the%20Mahakumbh%20stampede%20deaths%20till%20the%20President%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20did%20so.%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20accepted%20after%2017%20hours.%20These%20are%20people%20who%20cannot%20accept%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President's%20address%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20the%20'same%20old'%20points%2C%20and%20questioned%20the%20government's%20claims%20of%20development.%20On%20the%20government's%20Ease%20of%20Doing%20Business%20push%2C%20he%20said%20the%20government's%20ministers%20rush%20to%20every%20investment%20meet.%20%26quot%3BUttar%20Pradesh%20hosted%20a%20huge%20investment%20meet.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20the%20double-engine%20government%2C%20how%20much%20of%20the%20MoUs%20worth%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20has%20been%20implemented%20on%20the%20ground.%20Are%20the%20two%20engines%20colliding%20with%20each%20other%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20both%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20opinions%20on%20the%20border%20dispute%20with%20China.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20lost%20lakhs%20of%20acres%20to%20China%2C%20BJP%20is%20on%20the%20same%20path.%20But%20BJP%20does%20not%20accept%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20Census%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20once%20the%20Congress%20was%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20%26quot%3BNow%20Congress%20is%20with%20us.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20it%20was%20not.%20If%20Congress%20was%20with%20us%20then%2C%20we%20would%20not%20need%20to%20ask%20you%20now.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20Congress%2C%20we%20are%20your%20allies%20and%20we%20will%20back%20you%20on%20this%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0As%20BJP%20MPs%20started%20claiming%20rifts%20within%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20clash%2C%20not%20like%20your%20engines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kannauj%20MP%20said%20China%20is%20snatching%20not%20just%20land%2C%20but%20the%20market%20too.%20Referring%20to%20the%201991%20economic%20reforms%20under%20the%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Indian%20market%20was%20opened%20up%2C%20adequate%20attention%20was%20not%20paid%20to%20the%20economy.%20If%20the%20required%20focus%20would%20have%20been%20on%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%2C%20we%20would%20have%20surged%20ahead%20of%20China.%26quot%3B%20When%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20giving%20them%20gyan%20(advice)%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20track%20is%20the%20cycle's%20track.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738656840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Faolallao_yogi-akhilesh_625x300_05_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-they-claimed-digital-kumbh-couldnt-give-digits-of-dead-akhilesh-yadav-7630551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20claiming%20to%20have%20organised%20a%20digital%20Kumbh%20could%20not%20give%20digits%20to%20the%20casualties%20in%20the%20Prayagraj%20stampede%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20as%20he%20launched%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canoni