20declared%20as%20foreigners%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20waiting%20for%20some%20%26quot%3Bmuhurat%26quot%3B%20(auspicious%20time).%C2%A0The%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20asked%20the%20Assam%20government%20to%20deport%2063%20people%20currently%20in%20the%20detention%20centres%20after%20they%20were%20declared%20foreigners%20during%20the%20exercise%20to%20update%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20in%20the%20border%20state.%20The%20state%20argued%20that%20it%20did%20not%20know%20to%20address%20of%20the%20foreigners%20in%20their%20country%20of%20origin%2C%20but%20the%20court%20was%20not%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPulling%20up%20the%20state%20government%2C%20Justice%20Oka%20said%20Assam%20was%20suppressing%20facts.%20To%20this%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%20replied%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20highest%20authority%20of%20the%20Executive%20and%20apologised%20for%20%26quot%3Bsome%20lacunae%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20issue%20a%20perjury%20notice%20to%20you.%20You%20are%20supposed%20to%20come%20clean%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20state's%20counsel%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20intention%20to%20hide%26quot%3B.%20Justice%20Oka%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20there%20is.%20Why%20have%20you%20not%20given%20the%20dates%20on%20which%20verification%20took%20place%3F%20The%20affidavit%20is%20defective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhuyan%20weighed%20in.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20declare%20a%20person%20as%20a%20foreigner%2C%20you%20must%20take%20the%20next%20logical%20step.%20You%20can't%20detain%20them%20forever.%20Article%2021%20is%20there.%20There%20are%20many%20foreigner%20detention%20centres%20in%20Assam.%20How%20many%20have%20you%20deported%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrashing%20the%20state's%20response%20that%20the%20addresses%20of%20foreigners%20in%20their%20countries%20were%20not%20known%2C%20Justice%20Oka%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20deport%20them%20to%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20the%20country.%20Suppose%20the%20person%20is%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20you%20know%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Pakistan%3F%20How%20can%20you%20keep%20them%20detained%20here%20saying%20their%20foreign%20address%20is%20not%20known%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20foreigners%20must%20be%20deported%20at%20once.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20the%20status%20of%20their%20citizenship.%20Then%20how%20can%20you%20wait%20till%20their%20address%20is%20received%3F%20It%20is%20for%20the%20other%20country%20to%20decide%20where%20should%20they%20go.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Justice%20Oka%20asked%20Assam%20why%20it%20had%20not%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20seeking%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738654920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F01n469u8_supreme-court-of-india_625x300_12_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaiting-for-muhurat-supreme-court-asks-assam-to-deport-63-people-7630190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWaiting%20For%20Muhurat%3F%26quot%3B%20Supreme%20Court%20Asks%20Assam%20To%20Deport%2063%20People%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaiting-for-muhurat-supreme-court-asks-assam-to-deport-63-people-7630190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Man%20Survives%20Stage%204%20Cancer%20%26amp%3B%2012%20Chemo%20Rounds%3A%20Ready%20for%20New%20Beginning%20with%20Marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCancer%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20define%20you.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20battle%20that%20can%20be%20won%20with%20hope%20and%20determination%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harteij%20Bhartesh%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20lawyer%20from%20Rewa%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20cancer%20survivor%2C%