hich%20had%20an%20AQI%20of%20around%20120.%20At%20one%20point%20during%20the%20discussion%2C%20Mr%20Johnson%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20see%20you%20over%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20asked%20about%20India's%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfirming%20the%20incident%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Johnson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20in%20India%2C%20I%20did%20end%20this%20podcast%20early%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20air%20quality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20Mr%20Kamath%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgracious%20host%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%20the%20room%20was%20circulating%20outside%20air%2C%20rendering%20his%20air%20purifier%20ineffective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20he%20left%2C%20Mr%20Johnson%20noted%20the%20indoor%20AQI%20had%20climbed%20to%20130%2C%20with%20PM2.5%20levels%20at%2075%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%20-%20equivalent%20to%20smoking%203.4%20cigarettes%20over%2024%20hours.%20He%20added%20that%20after%20just%20three%20days%20in%20India%2C%20the%20pollution%20triggered%20a%20rash%2C%20along%20with%20persistent%20eye%20and%20throat%20irritation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Johnson%20criticised%20how%20deeply%20normalised%20air%20pollution%20has%20become%20in%20India.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20be%20outside%20running.%20Babies%20and%20small%20children%20exposed%20from%20birth.%20No%20one%20wore%20a%20mask%2C%20which%20can%20significantly%20decrease%20exposure.%20It%20was%20so%20confusing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20questioned%20why%20India's%20leadership%20had%20not%20declared%20air%20pollution%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20emergency%26quot%3B%20and%20cited%20studies%20on%20air%20pollution's%20health%20effects.%20%26quot%3BThe%20evidence%20shows%20that%20India%20would%20improve%20the%20health%20of%20its%20population%20more%20by%20cleaning%20up%20air%20quality%20than%20by%20curing%20all%20cancers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EOver%20To%20America%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20a%20com